Name: Description
Monthly Rent: The monthly rent (in dollars) agreed to or contracted for, regardless of any furnishings, utilities, fees, meals, or services that may be included.

Name: Source Notes
Monthly Rent: U.S. Census Bureau, American Community Survey 5-Year Estimates, Table B25056 (2009-2020);  retrieved from https://data.census.gov/.

Name: Notes
Monthly Rent: Percents refer to the percent of all occupied rental units.
